{With balanced distribution and 16 points NORTH should open 1NT rather than 1\D.

SOUTH's response is based on simple math. He adds his 18 points to the 15 minimum that NORTH has announced and 
comes up with 33 points combined. This is enough for a small slam, and since he has balanced distribution 
he bids 6NT.}

